      <title>【Bash Shell Script】強大的命令提示字元？</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/2019/05/bash-shell-script%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E5%AD%97%E5%85%83/</link>
